Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:19.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Woke up with yawning,\Nit's dawning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:22.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still alive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:27.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Turned on my radio\NTo start up new day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:30.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As goddamed D.J. chattered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:32.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:39.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing news got over\NOn that air wave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NLove is rationed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:45.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NAcross the nation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:49.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight\NLove reflects world wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:50.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Almost another day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:55.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's a shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.29,0:01:01.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good-night, good-night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:06.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's a shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:10.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:16.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NLove is rationed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:19.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NAcross the nation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:23.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight\NLove reflects world wide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:24.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Almost another day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:28.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See you some other day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:42.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Licht Schneide!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:46.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Getsugatensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:09.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:28.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:30.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:43.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:46.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to get me killed\Nas well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:49.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that you're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:51.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:03.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:16.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn… How is he able to\Nkeep up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:20.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not nearly as fast\Nas you are, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:24.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you could say it's my years\Nof fighting experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:26.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:27.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:31.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know which way you're going to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:33.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:43.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that your wind defense\Ncan't protect you against everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:51.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how good your defense is,\Nit's possible to harm you…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:56.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,if I use an attack that's more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:03.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're better than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:07.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…you still won't be able\Nto defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:13.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you… Soul Society is filled\Nwith concentrated reishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:16.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We Bounts are immortal here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:22.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then prove your immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:14.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's the face of\Nthat old lady, Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:26.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:29.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:30.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:33.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who…are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:36.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Rantao.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:37.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:42.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rantao…you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:43.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:50.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rantao… The creator of the Bounts\Nwho was exiled from Seireitei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:53.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:57.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! Are you really her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And…that face…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:04.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The attitude of the Soul Reapers\Nhas changed quite a bit, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:05.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:07.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So vulgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:13.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it enough proof that\NI know about the Bounts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:14.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:18.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who knows about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:21.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the Bounts other than\Nthe Soul Reapers of Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:25.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All the information on Bounts,\Nexcept for a small section…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:27.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,should have been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:33.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're…a Bount, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:38.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You know that I'm the real Rantao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:41.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can feel it, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:44.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd come some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:49.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've waited for\Na mind-numbingly long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:55.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed… It took a long time\Nto get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:08:00.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We Bounts have suffered\Na painfully long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:04.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And…are you the one\Nwho forced this upon us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:08.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're much more emotional\Nthan you look…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:12.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And more short-tempered\Nthan you sound…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:28.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of things I want to\Nask you if you’re really Rantao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:31.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:36.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who said I was going to kill her here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:37.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:43.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She has to watch us\Nachieve our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:47.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What happened as\Na result of her actions…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:52.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kill her…\Nafter I destroy Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:54.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:58.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:03.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you… I'll kill anyone who's\Nan enemy of Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:32.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that I can also break…\Nyour so-called wind defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya, let's pull back for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:00.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Koga…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dalk! Cause a disturbance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:08.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my. There are so many\Nhandsome men!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:13.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sorry. I can't play with you today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:41.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lirin, do you know where they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:47.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good… My sensors couldn't work\Nproperly in those explosions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:47.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:49.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:50.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to chase Kariya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:57.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He has already disappeared\Ninto the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:10:59.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that's it's pointless\Nto go after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:01.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Until the next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:07.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. Oh well…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:10.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an enemy?\NOr are you an ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:32.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are more people than\NI thought there'd be…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:37.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichinose, at this rate they'll continue\Nto double in number…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:39.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and will quickly grow\Ninto a huge crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:44.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this means there were a lot\Nwho were dissatisfied with Seireitei…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:49.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where did Kariya go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:52.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see Koga anywhere either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:54.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:10.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:11.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:15.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:20.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:23.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:26.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:32.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… It's Rantao,\Nthe one Yoruichi talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:36.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That outfit… A Quincy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:38.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world…is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:41.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Soul Reaper and a Quincy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:44.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty amusing combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:49.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going against the Bounts,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:52.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:57.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then could you tell us about the Bounts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:00.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Before that…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:02.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to\Ntend to your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My home is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:08.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can talk there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:18.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. All right, Bonnie, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:25.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think… He should be somewhere\Naround here…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ganju, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:52.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Bull of Kusajishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:55.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, Ganju?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:58.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:17.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Deal with it! I'm almost finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:24.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There. You're healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:25.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My wounds are healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:30.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:32.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate a technician!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:36.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So…what should I begin talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:41.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you know\Nabout the Bounts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You were using human souls to\Ndo experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:48.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to create a life that never dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:53.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that from the leader\Nof the Bounts, Kariya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:58.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya…I see.\NThat man earlier, he's the Bounts'…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:14:59.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:08.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The success rate of our experiment\Nshould have been very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:12.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there was an accident\Nduring the experiment…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:14.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that affected the cycle of rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:16.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's what created the Bounts,\Nwasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:31.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right… The Bounts had no place\Nin the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:34.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, they tried to rely\Non Soul Society, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:37.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Society didn't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:43.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Allowing Bounts in would mean\Naccepting their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:47.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That would mean admitting\Nthat they had created
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:50.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a subspecies as a side effect\Nof the experiment…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:55.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After being refused entrance…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:58.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the Bounts tried to force their way\Ninto Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:04.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And…that's when the Quincies\Nbecame involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:34.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Society took that chance and\Nnearly annihilated the Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:53.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who managed to escape or\Nwere living elsewhere during that battle…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,are Kariya's group right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:17:02.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you've gathered that much information,\Nwhat were you doing until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:05.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You created the Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:09.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you have gone to the World\Nof the Living and done something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:14.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're so concerned about\Nthe Bounts…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:19.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As a researcher,\Ndidn't you feel attached
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:22.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to the Bounts even if\Nthey were created by accident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:37.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My Soul Reaper power was\Nsealed away
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:40.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when I was exiled from Seireitei…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:44.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This includes going to\Nthe World of the Living…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:47.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even escape this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:52.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that power you used\Nto get between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:56.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After many years\Nand much research…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:18:00.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was finally able to get back enough\NSpiritual Pressure to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:05.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However…That's also limited…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:12.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But why were you the only one\Nexiled from Seireitei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:18.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The ones from Seireitei who exiled me…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,were relieved to learn that\Nthe Bounts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:23.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,didn't have the reishi\Nconversion ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:27.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did they think that everything could\Nbe settled in the World of the Living?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:30.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I predicted that the Bounts would
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:36.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,use any means they could\Nto come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:42.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I suggested we publicize\Neverything and accept the Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:45.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the result…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:46.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:52.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quincy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:57.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've caused you a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:01.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya used your power\Nto come here, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:04.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:06.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:12.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But why? The Bounts used\Nthe Quincy power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:16.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you are the Bounts’ ally\Nsince you helped them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:21.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But from what I can see,\Nyou seem to be their enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:23.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a lot has happened…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:31.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:35.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what kind\Nof tool that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:41.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That artifact is…incredibly dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you use it recklessly…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:51.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know. But I have to use this power\Nto defeat Kariya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:53.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:56.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You say that you're prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:02.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…\NBut be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:04.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure that you don't cause trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:07.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,not only for yourself,\Nbut to those around you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:09.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:11.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:15.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:21.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you think I looked strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:28.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite older than\Nmost Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:29.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:34.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\NI did things to myself as well…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:37.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in order to wait for\Nthe Bounts to come…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:41.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm going to rest\Nfor about half a day…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:42.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Half a day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:44.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:48.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I still have things to ask you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:52.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I recover. Until then…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:01.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she fell asleep…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:07.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. I was still talking…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:10.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She says she's a lot older\Nthan she looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:11.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:15.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:18.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to go back\Nto Kukaku's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:23.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, we still have things to ask her\Nwhen she wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:26.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to rest here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:29.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like the best thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:36.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How was Byakuya Kuchiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:42.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad… I think fighting him made\Nfor a good declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:45.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Was that your true goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:49.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've been inquiring\Ntoo much lately, Koga…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:52.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably because\NI'm in high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.20,0:22:01.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichinose!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:01.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:03.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the other three?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:08.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They are watching the movements\Nof Seireitei as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:11.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see… It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:12.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:12.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:31.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wanna lose!\NDon't wanna cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:34.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,'Cuz I wanna keep laughing!\NMOVIN'! MOVIN'!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:37.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wanna lose!\NDon't wanna cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:40.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,'Cuz I wanna keep laughing!\NMOVIN'! MOVIN'!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:46.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lying around, dozing as usual\NFlipping through nothing but manga books
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:49.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My motto: Funny & Easy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.28,0:22:51.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna live life carefree
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:54.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"On the road you need a companion,\Nin life you need sympathy"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:57.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Underneath the sun, smilin' every day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:02.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Being kind to others, and also to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:08.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I get things done\Nwhen I need to (Really?)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:14.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, come with me\N(Can I trust you?)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.25,0:23:17.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me or not, you won't really know\Nuntil you give it a try
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:20.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, wouldn't you rather trust\Nand laugh together?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:23.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,(I wanna) Go for walk
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:26.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Things won't get started\Nif you don't act!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:28.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wanna lose!\NDon't wanna cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.96,0:23:31.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,'Cuz I wanna keep laughing!\NMOVIN'! MOVIN'!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:34.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wanna lose!\NDon't wanna cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.82,0:23:37.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,'Cuz I wanna keep laughing!\NMOVIN'! MOVIN'!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:40.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wanna lose!\NDon't wanna cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.55,0:23:43.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,'Cuz I wanna keep laughing!\NMOVIN'! MOVIN'!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.30,0:23:46.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wanna lose!\NDon't wanna cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.26,0:23:49.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,'Cuz I wanna keep laughing!\NMOVIN'! MOVIN'!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.09,0:23:56.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is great that Rukia has\Nsuch a cool older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.32,0:23:58.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's reserved, calm, refined,\Nand incredibly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.63,0:24:01.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You mean he's inarticulate,\Ninsensitive, and arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:03.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter, Senbonzakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.31,0:24:06.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that you're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:08.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you went home…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.90,0:24:19.89,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers\NGolden after these messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.92,0:24:21.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.04,0:24:22.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.36,0:24:23.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A souvenir?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.27,0:24:24.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.43,0:24:25.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you regretted
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.69,0:24:29.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,there weren't any combs\Nthat were right for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.74,0:24:32.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So when I went to\Nthe World of the Living…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.99,0:24:33.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.85,0:24:37.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It looks quite different\Nfrom a regular comb…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.40,0:24:39.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.55,0:24:43.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… This is quite a rarity…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.95,0:24:45.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad he's happy…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.05,0:24:49.86,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,PET SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.35,0:24:49.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime Inoue knows good stores…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.87,0:24:57.87,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,HOW RUDE OF YOU TO ASK MY AGE!